gradle build how to

if you don't have gradle installed you can use the wrapper ( gradlew.bat or gradlew files in the project dir )

if using the wrapper replace gradle command with gradlew

#running a single test
gradle -Dserver.url=https://bard-qa.broadinstitute.org/BARD/ -Dgeb.env=firefox test -Dtest.single=PanelSpec

# or
gradle -Dserver.url=https://bard-qa.broadinstitute.org/BARD/ -Dgeb.env=firefox test -Dtest.single=*SummarySpec